4. Study popular fonts that used, usually the headings font is not the same as the paragraph font
5. Make sure all images have alt tag with text
6. Please add hover states (psuedo class :hover) change color
7. Project title should be h3 or h4
8. Don't put col- on img (mg should be inside) or any elements it should have its own or tag
9. Spacing between elements for project should be 30px or40px
10. Study Google Schema
11. For each section title, best to use h1 or h2
12. Responsiveness only needs to be 320px and up for sites
13. Please add to footer 2018-2019 Â© All Rights Reserved.
14. About me 4rem font-size for desktop/tablet, pixlr.com/express to change image with filter and subtlepatterns.com
to add a image background. 
15. header with background add background-attachment: fixed; for parallax effect
16. Navigation needs to be in a container
17. position: relative; overflow: hidden; study why to use
